  "original_title": "\u0d9c\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0dd4 \u0d9a\u0ddc\u0da7\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dda\u0daf\u0dd3 \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0ddd\u0db0\u0dad\u0dcf\u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0db1\u0dca \u0db6\u0dbd\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dcf \u0dc4\u0dd0\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dd0\u0dba\u0dd2 \u0db4\u0dd9\u0dad\u0dca\u0dc3\u0db8\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A petition that protestors were forcibly dispersed at Galle Fort",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A group of armed soldiers who came to the peaceful protest march in front of the Galle Fort against the current economic crisis, demanded Rs. 50 lakhs in compensation for the fundamental rights violated by the forcible dispersal of the protesters. ) Filed.",
        "Attorney-at-Law Amaradiwakara Liyanarachchi and former JVP MP Ajith Kumara have been named as respondents in the petition.",
        "The petition filed by Attorney-at-Law Manjula Manjula Balasuriya alleges that a group of armed Army personnel who had come to protest in Galle on the 30th had forcibly dispersed the protesters and that their fundamental rights had been violated.",
        "Due to this the petitioners have requested the court to hear this petition."
      ],
